<h5>Your Order Cancellation Rights</h5>
You are entitled to cancel Your Order within 7 days without giving any reason for doing so.<br>
You can also cancel your order anytime before dispatch. You need to go to your account and cancel the order and also need to mail us with subject <strong>CANCELLATION</strong><br>
<li>Shipping Charges will not be refunded.</li>
<li>The deadline for cancelling an Order is 7 days from the date on which You received the Goods or on which a third party you have appointed, who is not the carrier, takes possession of the product delivered.</li>
<li>In order to exercise Your right of cancellation, You must inform Us of your decision by means of a clear statement. You can inform us of your decision by:</li>
